<p class="fs-5 fw-300">An alternative citation manager for those already in the Mendeley ecosystem.</p>

<hr />

<h2 id="what-is-it-good-for">What is It Good For?</h2>

<p>Same problem as Zotero — organizing sources and generating citations — but in a different tool. If you’re already using Mendeley or your lab/advisor uses it, this guide will help you get more out of it.</p>

<p><strong>Where it fits in the workflow:</strong> Collect → Organize → Write &amp; Cite</p>

<hr />

